Fell Stinger 25 50 100 When the user knocks out a target with this move, the its Attack stat rises drastically.
First Impression 10 90 100 This move with great power only works the first turn each time the user enters battle.
Floral Flourish 20 70 100 A dancing whirl of flowers. Restores HP from the damage dealt in Floral Terrain.

Heal Order 10 — — The user calls out its underlings to heal it, regaining up to half of its max HP.
Infestation 20 20 100 The target is infested and attacked for four to five turns. It can't flee during this time.
Leech Life 10 80 100 The user drains the target's blood. The user's HP is restored by half the damage caused.
Lunge 15 80 100 The user makes a lunge at the target with full force. This also lowers its Attack stat.

Pin Missile 20 25 95 Sharp spikes are shot at the target in rapid succession two to five times in a row.

Pounce 20 50 100 The user attacks by pouncing on the target. This lowers the target's Speed stat.
Powder 20 — 100 The target is covered in a combustible powder that explodes from Fire-type moves.
Quiver Dance 20 — — The user performs a beautiful dance, boosting its Sp. Atk, Sp. Def, and Speed stats.
Rage Powder 20 — — The user scatters a cloud of irritating powder. Opposing Pokémon aim only at the user.
Signal Beam 15 75 100 The user attacks with a sinister beam of light. This may also confuse the target.

Silver Wind 5 60 100 Powdery scales blown by wind attack the target. This may also raise all the user's stats.
Skitter Smack 10 70 90 The user skitters behind the target to attack. This also lowers its Sp. Atk stat.
Spider Web 10 — — The user ensnares the target with thin, gooey silk so it can't flee from battle.
Steamroller 20 65 100 The user crushes its target with its rolled-up body. This may also make it flinch.
Sticky Web 20 — — The user weaves a sticky net around the opposing team, lowering Speed when switching.
String Shot 40 — 95 Opposing Pokémon are bound with silk that harshly lowers their Speed stats.
Struggle Bug 20 50 100 While resisting, the user attacks opposing Pokémon. This lowers their Sp. Atk stats.

Twineedle 20 25 100 The target is stabbed twice by a pair of stingers. It may also poison the target.
U-turn 20 70 100 After making its attack, the user rushes back to switch places with a party Pokémon.
X-Scissor 15 80 100 The target is slashed at by scythes or claws crossed as if they were a pair of scissors.
